column5: I have a vacancy in this roomy 804sq ft one-bathroom apartment at Wimberly Park Apts. This unit includes a dishwasher and a microwave.Connectors for your own full-size washer and dryer come installed in the laundry closet. The bedroom has a walk-in closet and comfortable,carpeting.The community location puts you just minutes from Dallas with easy access to Highway 35,67and Interstates 635 and 20. More information is just a phone call away!
